#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga "
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 27. Saññāsutta → pañcamabhikkhuaparibhāgiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Saññāsutta "
msgstr "27. Perceptions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.24, sc1
msgctxt "an7.27:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that prevent decline. "

msgctxt "an7.27:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha … pe …. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention … "

msgctxt "an7.27:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā? "
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that prevent decline? "

msgctxt "an7.27:1.4"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū aniccasaññaṃ bhāvessanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. "
msgstr "As long as the mendicants develop the perception of impermanence … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.27:2.1"
msgid "Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhū anattasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … pe … "
msgstr "not-self … "

msgctxt "an7.27:2.2"
msgid "asubhasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "ugliness … "

msgctxt "an7.27:2.3"
msgid "ādīnavasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "drawbacks … "

msgctxt "an7.27:2.4"
msgid "pahānasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "giving up … "

msgctxt "an7.27:2.5"
msgid "virāgasaññaṃ bhāvessanti … "
msgstr "fading away … "

msgctxt "an7.27:2.6"
msgid "nirodhasaññaṃ bhāvessanti; "
msgstr "cessation, "

#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.27:3.1"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. Yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā bhikkhūsu ṭhassanti, imesu ca sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu, bhikkhū sandississanti; vuddhiyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhūnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti. "
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline. As long as these seven principles that prevent decline last among the mendicants, and as long as the mendicants are seen following them, they can expect growth, not decline.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.27:3.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
